name: Lost Children of Andromeda: CYNQUE Archives - The Lost Time Research

metadata.name: Professor Adams' Lost Research
metadata.description:
Allister Adams, a young Evolutionary, lives at the edge of the apocalypse. There are 215 Days left until the end of humanity. Only one thing promises their salvation. With 7 hours, 16 minutes, and 13 seconds until another lost day, Allister discovers a few pages of looseleaf outside his RiserTown flat which has his father's missing research on it. 

He can't make sense of all of the symbols, the language, and the equations. He believes if he can find the rest of the research, he can discover what his father is trying to tell him. 

This is page 1 of ____.
